== 可用性 ==
据[[朝鲜中央电视台|朝鲜中央电视台]]（KCTV）的报道，「万方」的服务范围不仅局限在[[平壤|平壤]]，还为[[沙里院市|沙里院]]和[[新義州市|新义州]]的公民提供服务。KCTV指出，这些地区对万方IPTV的需求极高，使用此服务的人有数百名。 <ref name="NKNews">{{Cite news|url=https://www.nknews.org/2016/08/netflix-style-video-on-demand-comes-to-north-korea-state-tv-shows/|title=Netflix style video-on-demand comes to North Korea, state TV shows|first=Dagyum|author=Ji|work=NK News|publisher=Korea Risk Group|date=18 August 2016|accessdate=25 August 2016|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160825123938/https://www.nknews.org/2016/08/netflix-style-video-on-demand-comes-to-north-korea-state-tv-shows/|archivedate=25 August 2016}}</ref><ref>{{Citation|title=北朝鮮 「ネットTVマルチメディア閲覧機『マンバン』 (망TV다매체열람기 《만방》)」 KCTV 2016/08/16 日本語字幕付き|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kVZ2mO6UEA4|accessdate=2022-01-21|language=zh-CN|archive-date=2022-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220121182900/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kVZ2mO6UEA4|dead-url=no}}</ref>

